128
00:07:29,932 --> 00:07:32,813
It's important that you're able to jump around and play something else.

129
00:07:33,789 --> 00:07:38,631
because if I guess the best way to explain this is with other games if you're stuck in a game like

130
00:07:38,711 --> 00:07:43,413
super meat boy every time you fail in super meat boy you at least feel like you're getting better

131
00:07:43,493 --> 00:07:47,575
you feel like your skill is progressing when you fail in a puzzle game you don't ever feel

132
00:07:47,596 --> 00:07:52,118
like your skill is progressing you've either you've figured out the puzzle or you have not

133
00:07:52,178 --> 00:07:55,940
figured out the puzzle and if you're not if you haven't figured out the puzzle you don't feel

