150
00:09:07,723 --> 00:09:12,807
So if I had a sketchy art style, I could have a line that kind of overhangs the world, and I could have the...

151
00:09:13,567 --> 00:09:17,969
I could show the grid of the world in negative space so that the player could actually see the

152
00:09:18,029 --> 00:09:23,511
board that they were playing on. Another thing I locked down as far as the art goes was the

153
00:09:23,651 --> 00:09:30,453
character design which seems, I guess, obvious in hindsight but the characters had to be designed

